config_file_add:
export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/jdk
export JRE_HOME=${JAVA_HOME}/jre
export CLASSPATH=.:${JAVA_HOME}/lib:${JRE_HOME}/lib
export PATH=${JAVA_HOME}/bin:$PATH
cygwin_config_add:
@echo off
set _T=%CD%
echo %_T
D:
chdir D:\cygwin64\bin
@rem bash --login -i
start mintty.exe -e /bin/bash --login -i
cygwin_bash_add:
export _T=${_T//\\//}
if [ $_T == "" ]; then
export _T=~
fi
cd "$_T"
